| [[White-throated Kingfisher]] || [[File:White-throated Kingfisher (Shankar).jpg|50px]]
|-
| '''State  tree'''
| [[Devil Tree]]<ref name="wiisymbols"/>|| [[File:Alstonia scholaris.jpg|50px]]
